      %b Taxon Information.  
      %span.c0 Taxa below superkingdom level are associated with a classification hierarchy.  Every taxon is associated with a scientific name.  The total number of families is an integer calculated from the FALO classification and is only shown for taxa above the rank family. The taxon source is a string, specifically referenced in FALO classification.  
